    Resource monitor contain cloud infrastructure resource capacity statics.
It list statics based on zones,pod,cluster,host. 

 !adminguide/cloud/10.png!

 {code}

Statics of *zone,pod and cluster* contain following items 
with percentage of allocated and free resources.

  Memory,Cpu,Storage,Primary storage Allocated,Public Ip address,
Management Ip address,secondary storage,Vlan,Shared network ips,
Local storage.

Statics of *Host* contain following items with percentage 
of allocated and free resources.

   Total Cpu,Cpu utilized,Cpu allocated for Vms,Memory Total,Memory Allocated,
Memory Used, Network Read,Network Write.

